【Experienced Adventurer A】 You know about magic, right? Well, it's
pretty important when it comes to dungeon exploration.

【Experienced Adventurer A】 That's talent, you know. The energy needed
to use magic, MP, seems to be determined by the total amount you're
born with.

【Experienced Adventurer A】 In other words, those without MP can't use
magic and will never be able to use it in their lifetime.

【Experienced Adventurer A】 It seems that there are some external
factors that can grant MP... but it seems I didn't have the talent or
luck for that. It's a cruel story, huh.

【Former Adventurer Customer】 Hey, I heard you're an adventurer. I used
to be one too, but I retired. I found something worth protecting, you
know. Hehe.

【Former Adventurer Customer】 I couldn't afford to die anymore, so
here's a piece of advice. You can't escape from monsters in the
dungeon, basically.

【Former Adventurer Customer】 Well, the interior is not only difficult
to see through but also structurally complex. No matter how blindly
you run around, you'll just end up being outmaneuvered.

【Former Adventurer Customer】 If only \c[18] smoke bombs \c[0] were
available, it would be a different story. Thanks to the smoke, the
opponent loses sight of us too. In that opening, we can escape.

【Former Adventurer Customer】 Make sure to always have it with you when
entering the dungeon, okay?

熟練冒険者
chara_10_03

【Experienced Adventurer】 Weapons have their own characteristics, you
know. It's best to use something that's easy to use.

【Experienced Adventurer】 First, let's talk about swords. The
characteristic of a sword is that you can \C[18] parry and
counterattack \C[0] immediately.

【Experienced Adventurer】 When there are multiple opponents, this
becomes quietly effective.

【Experienced Adventurer】 Next, let's talk about maces. The
characteristic of a mace is that it occasionally \C[18]stuns\C[0] the
opponent.

【Experienced Adventurer】 If you manage to stun your opponent, you can
beat even the strongest enemies with ease. However, be careful as
there are monsters that cannot be stunned. Slimes are a prime example
of that.

【Experienced Adventurer】 Lastly, let's talk about daggers. The
characteristic of a dagger is \C[18] inflicting damage on the opponent
through bleeding \C[0].

【Experienced Adventurer】 The attack power of daggers itself is low,
but sometimes you can find daggers that have poison or burning
effects. So, if you find one, try using it.

【Experienced Adventurer】 It should have more power than it looks.
However, be careful as you won't be able to equip a shield for
defense.

【Experienced Adventurer】 That's about it. Well, understanding the
characteristics of weapons and choosing the right one is the key to
conquering dungeons. Good luck!
